# Jira Operating Rules

- For each story:
  - Fetch acceptance criteria, post a short implementation plan
  - Transition to In Progress upon starting; attach branch name
  - Add a compliance comment before PR, and after merge if needed
- Prefer the highest-priority To Do story; create branch from develop
- Use issue key in branch and PR title; link PR in Jira

